title: dbAccess Taiwan Semiconductor and Automotive Corporate Day
body:
This corporate day focuses on Taiwan semiconductor and automotive companies, and will provide our clients with a better understanding of Taiwan’s semiconductor industry and the Tesla supply chain. The event offers meetings with management from the foundry, PCB and key automotive part sectors, and also provides an update on the competitive landscape of the various sectors.
We have invited a number of high-profile speakers from leading companies to present their views.
